1. Install jdk7
2. Install maven, git
3. Create github account if none
4. Git clone from https://github.com/schastny/votemeup.git
5. >cd votemeup
6. >mvn tomcat:run
7. Open localhost:8080/voteme in browser
8. Install SpringToolSuite (STS) from http://spring.io/tools/sts/
9. Install some MySQL 5
10. Create initial DB schema and populate it with some data

misc
consider looking through docs/progit.en.pdf and docs/MasteringSpringMVC3.pdf 
to get top level overview of SpringMVC and git.
SCJP Kathy Sierra